{"tid":747232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謎迷國情揭露：港獨分子猶如黑社會強姦犯，叫人如何桿衛他們的自由？","createTime":"2018-07-18T08:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T14:45:55.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6abec1a0e228990ad7a649fa81ab82b9639b4125","tid":747232,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5wL_tCVQ_mY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5wL_tCVQ_mY&d=fGgTHmipv3bGgdzButwhijOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=27ee350a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5wL_tCVQ_mY</a><br />\n內容大網：中共借陳浩天港獨打開了缺口，企圖進一步消滅自決派眾志。<br />\n本土港獨九死一生，無錯結社自由言論自由非常重要，是需要桿衛，但港獨分子，民族分子猶如黑社會，試問如何叫人捍衛黒社會強姦犯的自由呢？<br />\n<br />\n相反眾志年青人有勇氣，有熱情，得民心，相信有很多人願意為他們發聲。"},{"pid":"9faa1612f20a5ee974f9d821c5228808397bf947","tid":747232,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf75415809e30affdcfd7e8f38acc07a20987e10","tid":747232,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"其實點解樓主開親post都咁多錯字?"},{"pid":"1d263bf02af8ed7f7f43f7558376e383d7c4e90a","tid":747232,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccf5ebd41bbffde7017fd0585d15d04c4dbdaf7","tid":747232,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦<br />\n<br />\n泛民班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}